{"tid":335150,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"（鋼琴新手）想問下你地點練好拍子同節奏感？","createTime":"2017-07-25T11:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T12:21:26.000Z","uid":131157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5efa4d5217abfbd3272df42b7ed561e1d021337","tid":335150,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:01:32.000Z","msg":"如題，想問下你地係咪彈果陣心入面係咪一路數住1 and 2 and 3 and 咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之唔知點解我係會愈陣愈快，d 拍子亂曬，有冇方法可以練好呢方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbc9543e63863dc884e6786b65ccdfa34a96ada","tid":335150,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"自己數緊係唔準啦，用拍子機呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1acc29fd556ce22a1720997dcfc75107a11149","tid":335150,"uid":21462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"跟拍子機練習、彈一啲練習曲<br />\n有時肉眼分唔清個節奏係點就會用1ena2ena拆<br />\n肯定節奏岩就開始對拍子機練 handle唔到就再較慢啲<br />\n唔急得 一定要慢慢、逐步黎"},{"pid":"97657acb5bf51c55484cec2ba9ad7d9fa72ce0e5","tid":335150,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:15:40.000Z","msg":"平時聽歌數下拍子，跟住個節奏move下，要全身投入去感受拍子，唔好個心一直諗：12341234，死數拍子唔會對節奏感有幫助。同埋一定要放鬆，拍子節奏係音樂一部分，感受一下，每一拍都係觸動緊你，會不知不覺跟住郁。<br />\n<br />\n練琴就係跟拍子機練，電子拍子機會比較準，練嘅時候要仔細聽左先，係心入面數幾拍，同埋試下跟個拍子數「蘋果蘋果」、「士多啤梨」（16分音），咁你彈嘅時候就會平均少少。如果都係捉摸唔到，試下調一調拍子機，由數1拍變半拍，拆細黎數（對），會易d上手。"},{"pid":"353f099f6ef5dd068260e28d2e8fb45347d6e2ac","tid":335150,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時聽歌數下拍子，跟住個節奏move下，要全身投入去感受拍子，唔好個心一直諗：12341234，死數拍子唔會對節奏感有幫助。同埋一定要放鬆，拍子節奏係音樂一部分，感受一下，每一拍都係觸動緊你，會不知不覺跟住郁。<br />\n<br />\n練琴就係跟拍子機練，電子拍子機會比較準，練嘅時候要仔細聽左先，係心入面數幾拍，同埋試下跟個拍子數「蘋果蘋果」、「士多啤梨」（16分音），咁你彈嘅時候就會平均少少。如果都係捉摸唔到，試下調一調拍子機，由數1拍變半拍，拆細黎數（對），會易d上手。</blockquote><br />\nthz <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cba3d42833ce28444d202e252e3373b42bab27","tid":335150,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己數緊係唔準啦，用拍子機呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚會變左太依賴拍子機，冇理由次次彈都要開個拍子機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be33c1b189547ad8e4dcb5d38c854593e7f8c2f3","tid":335150,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cc5471ad32f133b3b2d6406cec1a2bb4c9420db","tid":335150,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自己數緊係唔準啦，用拍子機呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我驚會變左太依賴拍子機，冇理由次次彈都要開個拍子機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你練琴係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n彈得多慣左就得<br />\n<br />\n就好似背譜咁，唔洗死背<br />\n彈得多就自然記得</blockquote><br />\nic thz <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7f4b78257cb3